2025-06-20AAFCFarm Income Protection ActOrder amending Annex A of the Sustainable Canadian Agricultural PartnershipOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to amend Annex A of the Sustainable Canadian Agricultural Partnership, a Federal-Provincial-Territorial Framework Agreement on Agriculture, Agri-Food and Agri-based Products Policy in order to increase the compensation rate and increase the maximum payment amount for the 2025 program year.N/A
subject: Order amending Annex A of the Sustainable Canadian Agricultural Partnership
precis: Order authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to amend Annex A of the Sustainable Canadian Agricultural Partnership, a Federal-Provincial-Territorial Framework Agreement on Agriculture, Agri-Food and Agri-based Products Policy in order to increase the compensation rate and increase the maximum payment amount for the 2025 program year.
